Resource Profile: openIMIS CoverageEligibilityResponse

Official URL: https://github.com/openimis/openimis_fhir_r5_ig/StructureDefinition/openimis-coverage-eligibility-response Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2025-08-26 Computable Name: OpenIMISCoverageEligibilityResponse

Defines a CoverageEligibilityResponse for openIMIS to get the enquire information for an Insuree.

Usages:

  • Examples for this Profile: CoverageEligibilityResponse/JoeDoeEnquiringResponse
